    "readme_content": "# epstein-files\n\n* https://github.com/randallscott25-star/epstein-forensic-finance\n* https://github.com/yung-megafone/Epstein-Files\n* https://github.com/beak2825/epstein-files-archive\n* https://github.com/rhowardstone/Epstein-research\n\n## index-based search:\n* https://www.epsteinlibrary.org/\n\n## ai-assisted search:\n* https://searchepsteinfiles.com/ -- developing image search\n* https://epstein.lasearch.app/ -- fast\n* https://www.epsteinunboxed.com/ -- has image search\n* https://standardworks.ai/public-archives/epstein-files/documents -- 50-result search limit\n* https://epstein-data.com/\n\n## multi-function explorers:\n* https://epsteinexposed.com -- recent and now crowd-funded\n* https://epsteinalysis.com -- facial analysis/search\n* https://epsteingraph.com -- has image search\n* https://epsteinweb.org -- includes community chat\n* https://epstein-docs.github.io\n* https://epsteinsecrets.com/ -- requires account\n* https://svetimfm.github.io/epstein-files-visualizations/\n* https://epsteinvisualizer.com/\n* https://trackthefiles.org/\n* https://epsteinfilez.com/\n\n## new GUIs\n* https://jmail.world -- modern app layouts (youtube, facebook, iMessage, gmail, etc)\n* https://epstein.mobi/ -- mobile/text\n* https://jinder.world -- includes matchmaking algo for searching docs\n\n## chat agents\n* https://epsteingpt.com/\n* https://agents.vectorize.io/agents/7d84aa5d-84ab-4991-b268-0b379983f57a/chat\n* https://uncovered.today/\n\n## academic papers referenced in files\n* https://jeescholar.com/\n\n## memory builder\n* https://epsteindlegame.com/ -- which individual has more references in files\n\n## community forums\n* https://epsteinforums.org/index.php -- active community and multiple resources\n\n## interactive timelines\n* https://www.epsteintimeline2026.com/\n\n## community wikis\n* https://corroborators.wiki/wiki/Main_Page\n\n## time series analysis of file changes\n* https://justice.geeken.dev/\n\n## financial networking\n* https://tommycarstensen.com/epstein/money_network.html\n\n## dataset torrent magnets\n* https://lemmy.world/post/42440468\n* https://www.reddit.com/r/DataHoarder/comments/1qv4elx/doj_just_removed_all_epstein_zip_files_in_the/\n\n## additional DOJ/gov releases\n* https://epsteinforums.org/viewtopic.php?t=6\n"
